D E C E M B E R
A year in pictures. 
12/12 'Ruth'
London.
-

I was  lucky enough to end the year working with the super talented @am_antolin and @paulromeromendez who directed the short-film "Ruth" for the @arri and @directors_uk Trinity Challenge (#trinitychallenge). I couldn't think of a better caper for the year.
The film is is about Ruth whose dementia causes her to lose herself and her loved ones in her own home. .
